---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service - MA Cannabis Directory"
  description="Data usage terms and policies for the Massachusetts Cannabis Directory."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm text-green-700 hover:text-green-900 underline">&larr; Back to directory</a>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">About This Data</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        The information in this directory is sourced from Massachusetts Cannabis Control Commission (MCC) public records
        and supplemented by manual research. Data is updated periodically but not in real time, so it may contain
        inaccuracies or not reflect recent changes in ownership, licensing, or business operations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Using This Directory</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        This is a free public resource. You are welcome to reference and share information from this directory with
        attribution. The underlying dataset is not available for commercial resale.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">No Warranty</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        All data is provided as-is, without warranty of any kind. The publisher is not liable for inaccuracies
        or for any decisions made based on information in this directory.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Corrections and Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        If you spot an error, you can suggest a correction using the form on any listing page.
        This directory is published by
        <a href="https://meredithmcgee.org" class="text-green-700 hover:text-green-900 underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meredith McGee</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-12 border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">Last updated: March 2026</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
